<div class="cell shrink">
  <h1>{{model.filename}}</h1>
</div>
<div class="cell auto grid-x grid-padding-x">
  <div class="cell small-6 cell-block-container">
    <div class="cell shrink">
      <ul class="tabs">
        <li class="tabs-title is-active"><a href="#" onclick={{action "select-tab-panel" "#file-metadata"}} aria-selected="true">Metadata</a></li>
        <li class="tabs-title"><a href="#" onclick={{action "select-tab-panel" "#file-annotations"}}>Annotations</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="cell auto cell-block-y">
      <div class="tabs-content full-height">
        <div id="file-metadata" class="tabs-panel is-active full-height">
          <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x full-height">
            <div class="cell small-6 cell-block-y">
              <ul class="no-bullet">{{xml-tree-editor node=model.header click-node-title=(action "select-metadata-node") notify-model-change=(action "notify-model-change")}}</ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cell small-6 cell-block-y">
              {{#if selected_metadata_node}}
                {{node-editor node=selected_metadata_node edit_tail=false notify-model-change=(action "notify-model-change")}}
              {{/if}}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="file-annotations" class="tabs-panel full-height">
          <p>Suspendisse dictum feugiat nisl ut dapibus.  Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat molestie vehicula. Ut in nulla enim. Phasellus molestie magna non est bibendum non venenatis nisl tempor.  Sed auctor neque eu tellus rhoncus ut eleifend nibh porttitor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cell small-6 full-height">
    {{body-editor body=model.body}}
  </div>
</div>
